       Identification Division.
       Program-Id.                                 acrobat            .
      *================================================================*
      *                                                                *
      * Driver stampante : PostScript generico modulo verticale oppure *
      *                    orizzontale, a seconda dell'ampiezza riga.  *
      *                                                                *
      *                    Vedi driver 'psua4' per le specifiche       *
      *                                                                *
      *                    In base al canale di uscita in stampa,      *
      *                    viene o meno richiesto il nome del file di  *
      *                    destinazione per l'output in accordo con    *
      *                    il programma Acrobat Distiller (Rel. 4.0)   *
      *                                                                *
      *                    ___ ELIMINARE ___                           *
      *                                                                *
      *================================================================*

      ******************************************************************
       Environment Division.
      ******************************************************************

      *================================================================*
       Configuration Section.
      *================================================================*

       Source-Computer.     d-K-b-Snc-PD .
       Object-Computer.     d-K-b-Snc-PD .

       Special-Names.       Decimal-Point is comma .

      *================================================================*
       Input-Output Section.
      *================================================================*

       File-Control.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [stp]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select optional   stp   assign to input-output   f-stp-pat
                             organization is line sequential
                             access  mode is sequential
                             file status  is                f-stp-sts .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [pss]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select  optional  pss   assign to disk         f-pss-pat
                             organization is indexed
                             access mode  is dynamic
                             record key   is pss-key
                             file status  is f-pss-sts                .

