           perform   emi-seq-fin-000      thru emi-seq-fin-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori : uscita                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to spl-cls-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close file [stp]                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cls-stp-000          thru cls-stp-999            .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori in close [stp] : uscita               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to spl-cls-999.
       spl-cls-999.
           exit.

