           move      p-buf-lin (w-lin)    to   stp-rec                .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura record di [stp]                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-stp-000      thru wrt-rec-stp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori : uscita                              *
