      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione pathname file [stp]                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-pat-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Canale di uscita della stampante                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      p-sel-can-stp        to   f-stp-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione del nome file                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-pth-fil-000      thru acc-pth-fil-999        .
       det-pat-stp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura effettiva record [stp]                          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-rec-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione i-o status                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Write                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           write     stp-rec                                          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori in write                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        e-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to wrt-rec-stp-999.
